Title: Directs the metropolitan transportation authority and the New York city transit authority to rename the Jamaica Center- Parsons/Archer subway station
Summary: Directs the metropolitan transportation authority and the New York city transit authority to rename the Jamaica Center- Parsons/Archer subway station to the Jamaica Center- Parsons/ Archer York College Jamaica station.
ActClause: AN ACT directing the metropolitan transportation authority and the New York city transit authority to rename the Jamaica Center- Parsons/ Archer subway station to the Jamaica Center- Parsons/ Archer York College Jamaica station; and provides for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
